query:
SELECT id, name, description, date, time 
FROM trip_routes 
WHERE tripId = 30001 
AND (name = 'Liptovský Mikuláš → Štrbské Pleso' OR name = 'Liptovský Mikuláš → Demänovská Ice Cave')
ORDER BY date;
